content: Xiao Han is a senior undergraduate student at the College of Information Science & Electronic Engineering (ISEE), Zhejiang University (ZJU). He is currently working at the Artificial Intelligence & Robotics Lab (AiR) of Westlake Institute for Advanced Study (WIAS)as a research intern, advised by Dr. Changbin Yu. Previously, he was a visiting student of the University of Michigan (UMich), supervised by Prof. L. Jay Guo.
